  <title>Introduction</title>

  <p><app>Epiphany</app> is the GNOME web browser. It displays webpages with
  the same same speed and accuracy as other popular browsers, while respecting
  your privacy by default.</p>

  <p>In GNOME 3, <app>Epiphany</app> is also known as <app>Web</app>.</p>

